{"tid":2032673,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"點解泛民既行動永遠好似慢三拍咁？","createTime":"2020-05-24T07:35:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T10:47:51.000Z","uid":21470,"like":19,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8efc779c3d31f256923e3cfe684b092163f3209f","tid":2032673,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:35:31.000Z","msg":"Chin Ya<br />\n<br />\n望住d黃絲有時候我都覺得無奈同可笑。<br />\n<br />\n舊年話香港抗爭路線要巴結美國，佢地就話唔需要，話要行國際線路，阿何韻詩仲屌柒特朗普，自己走去中國揸樁既聯合國演講巧威威，好啦玩到今日推國安法，先來支持美國乜乜乜。<br />\n有時候點解黃絲既行動永遠好似慢三拍咁？要推分離主義時候佢同你講推動民主中國；要勇武抗爭時候佢同你講和理非；要種族分類時候佢話你法西斯唔大愛......<br />\n永遠同真正既時機錯摸，浪費晒d犧牲者......唉！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkchanyan/posts/10159711135044128\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkchanyan%2Fposts%2F10159711135044128&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtSPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=0300021f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkchanyan/posts/10159711135044128</a>"},{"pid":"6bb119af5bcff34dc4afce2d924c18a57a9fc366","tid":2032673,"uid":155012,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:36:50.000Z","msg":"剩係知仲有心情籌撚緊錢"},{"pid":"14d0c4d8a21994ce87e14fc392c6741bc05a6c3d","tid":2032673,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:38:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"332e3368c74e0131d5445756fcc562f7724ff804","tid":2032673,"uid":304769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:38:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位，連登黑色五毛風向警告</span><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登紅色五毛分化警告</span><br />\n宜家班死五毛<span style=\"color: red;\">除左用鬥黃進行分化，仲用扮演移民/留守派黎進行分化</span>，大家請保持獨立思考<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後大家要幫手簽個聯署支持BNO平權救手足</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtSPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=162e7d2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"cb72116ca0bf0a63df45d361bd6cf300898a202d","tid":2032673,"uid":31841,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:39:09.000Z","msg":"販民要呃飯食<br />\n垃會議員十幾萬一個月"},{"pid":"61c9bd2c496aec75bfbbb66005b4ab1c351468f2","tid":2032673,"uid":82082,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:43:19.000Z","msg":"泛民無執政意志，只有執錢意志<br />\n佢地係一班好想做議會公務員的一群<br />\n上家做左，有先例，安全啦，先會跟<br />\n佢地唔係諗點先成功，係諗點先安全，所以咪要睇人地做左先學囉，同政府班官/公務員作風一樣"},{"pid":"55a1bbe558889525d622594575501f3b123298cd","tid":2032673,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:45:14.000Z","msg":"可能因為北京離香港有d遠<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"c848ca0062c313eda6c9f81972cf96ad5bade5d2","tid":2032673,"uid":335897,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:48:08.000Z","msg":"因為佢地要撞過板先知唔得"},{"pid":"9880e78cb31621b8d41db7ee236321ecf745efd3","tid":2032673,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,